The '''Afterburners''' was a [[Swoop gang/Legends|swoop gang]] based on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Entralla/Legends|Entralla]] during the formative years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. They were led by an individual called [[Ace (swooper)|Ace]].

The Afterburners were commonly found lurking in the streets of the [[Overhang]], near [[Nexus City]]'s [[Spaceport/Legends|starport]], and would attempt to protect citizens from con men and other local criminals.

